<div id="help-text" class="alert alert-info">
	<a class="close" data-dismiss="alert" href="#">&times;</a>
	<h4 class="alert-heading"><%= link_to "Create Your First Reminder", :controller => "reminders" %></h4>
	
		<p>The reminders feature is designed to assist in following up labs/studies for patients
		recently discharged or seen in clinic. Once a reminder is due you will receive a page
		daily reminding you to check on the study.</p>
		<p>You can also text reminders to <b><%= number_to_phone(ENV['TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER'], :area_code => true)%></b> using your cell phone. Please make sure
		your text messages include a 7 digit MRN, and when to remind you. Examples:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>5671234 Check coags in 6 hours</li>
			<li>In 1 week check secondary HTN w/u 5231234</li>
			<li>Follow up blood cultures for 5123212 in 1 day</li>
		</ul>
</div>